{"tha-ap465:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap465:0.2":"Salakusumiyavagga ","tha-ap465:0.3":"Citakanibbapakattheraapadana ","tha-ap465:1.1":"“Dayhamane sariramhi, ","tha-ap465:1.2":"vessabhussa mahesino; ","tha-ap465:1.3":"Gandhodakam gahetvana, ","tha-ap465:1.4":"citam nibbapayim aham. ","tha-ap465:2.1":"Ekatimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap465:2.2":"citam nibbapayim aham; ","tha-ap465:2.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap465:2.4":"gandhodakassidam phalam. ","tha-ap465:3.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap465:3.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap465:3.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap465:4.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap465:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap465:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap465:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap465:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap465:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap465:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma citakanibbapako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap465:7.1":"Citakanibbapakattherassapadanam tatiyam. "}